Available Tools: list_inventory | restock_item | get_low_stock | update_price
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "slot_id": "string", "quantity": number, "price": number }
Response Schema: { "inventory": [{ "slot_id": "string", "name": "string", "quantity": number, "price": number }] }

Question: Identify which products are below the safety limit in the library break room machine.
Call: { "func_call": "get_low_stock", "slot_id": "", "quantity": 0, "price": 0 }
Response: { "inventory": [{ "slot_id": "J1", "name": "Green Tea", "quantity": 1, "price": 1.20 }, { "slot_id": "J2", "name": "Rice Cake", "quantity": 2, "price": 0.85 }] }

Question: Modify the cost of the Dark Chocolate in slot K4 to $2.80 following a tax adjustment.
Call: { "func_call": "update_price", "slot_id": "K4", "quantity": 0, "price": 2.80 }
Response: { "inventory": [{ "slot_id": "K4", "name": "Dark Chocolate", "quantity": 14, "price": 2.80 }] }

